{"tid":1190670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係支持引渡？","createTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T04:52:03.000Z","uid":176442,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec29a3f5c50983ec3fd7d99b8c7a66888eed9166","tid":1190670,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支持將孟晚舟引渡到美國</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大卑詩省最高法院周四（6日）起一連5天開庭討論引渡孟晚舟的技術問題，法庭接納孟晚舟代表律師的建議，排期於明年1月展開引渡聆訊，預期引渡聆訊將於明年10月或11月完結。<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師表示，期望案件在兩年內完結，又稱案件複雜，所需的處理時間將可能是一項「紀錄」。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大去年12月應美國要求，在溫哥華機場拘捕孟晚舟。"},{"pid":"8944ad8613797fa62ce49911dd4cd3362a93df89","tid":1190670,"uid":176442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:44:18.000Z","msg":"無？"},{"pid":"4543da7119a6be0f5cb909b077eb254b818b1b8d","tid":1190670,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4093bd78483fee2df44397792713048978df88","tid":1190670,"uid":52358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"支持超渡"},{"pid":"b5de2b87c22aa83ce60e2d71a78b51a68885c8cc","tid":1190670,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T13:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed8c5b9e1da28ce334d906ea97162b2d642cc9b","tid":1190670,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b1ab935289ae28b71690616f8c0d102c4cf886","tid":1190670,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc